147
00:11:22.466 --> 00:11:23.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
朝飯まだなんだろ？

148
00:11:25.066 --> 00:11:27.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うちで食ってってくれよ

149
00:11:27.633 --> 00:11:30.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
俺… 悪いからさ

150
00:11:30.100 --> 00:11:33.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
