151
00:11:36.300 --> 00:11:37.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
フフッ

152
00:11:38.733 --> 00:11:40.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おまちどおさん

153
00:11:56.533 --> 00:11:57.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あったまるね

154
00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:05.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（アナウンサー）映画「川歌」の
