155
00:12:05.300 --> 00:12:08.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
主演の風見倫子さんらが
抱負を語りました

156
00:12:09.566 --> 00:12:15.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（倫子）主人公の境遇と私の境遇が
重なるところがあって―

157
00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:19.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
自分の経験を この役に―

158
00:12:19.666 --> 00:12:23.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
全て注ぎ込めたらと思っています

159
00:12:23.300 --> 00:12:25.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
風見倫子か

160
00:12:26.133 --> 00:12:27.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いいよな この子

161
00:12:28.833 --> 00:12:31.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
