162
00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:34.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ゆうべも来ててさ

163
00:12:34.966 --> 00:12:38.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
でも注文するのは
いつも決まっててさ

164
00:12:39.233 --> 00:12:42.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ソース焼そばの目玉焼き載せ

165
00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:45.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ハハッ よっぽど好きなんだろうな

166
00:12:50.233 --> 00:12:51.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
