167
00:12:52.633 --> 00:12:56.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
焼そばに 四万十川(しまんとがわ)の
青のりかけるとうまいんだよ

168
00:12:57.366 --> 00:12:59.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
へえ そうなのかい

169
00:13:00.466 --> 00:13:02.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
風味が全然 違うんだよ

170
00:13:05.933 --> 00:13:08.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
今度あの子 来たら
かけてやってよ

171
00:13:10.466 --> 00:13:11.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）そうするよ

172
00:13:11.733 --> 00:13:14.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（茂樹）四万十川の青のりだよ

173
00:13:14.966 --> 00:13:15.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ああ

174
00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:30.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うまいな

175
00:13:31.733 --> 00:13:32.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
生き返る

176
00:13:37.633 --> 00:13:38.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（倫子）お父さん

177
00:13:40.033 --> 00:13:44.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
なんであの時
あたしのこと 捨てたの？

178
00:13:45.933 --> 00:13:47.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（男優）それは…

179
00:13:49.200 --> 00:13:52.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お父さんがいたから あたし…

180
00:13:53.433 --> 00:13:54.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（監督）カット
（助監督）はい カット

181
00:13:55.633 --> 00:13:57.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
ちょっと いったん時間置こう
（助監督）はい

182
00:13:57.533 --> 00:13:59.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
