186
00:14:20.166 --> 00:14:21.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
はい

187
00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:30.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
