188
00:14:32.500 --> 00:14:33.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
すみません

189
00:14:34.633 --> 00:14:37.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
