俺 イヤだって言ったんだよ

197
00:15:22.133 --> 00:15:25.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
おい 俺 妥協しねえからな
絶対 妥協しねえからな おい

198
00:15:25.766 --> 00:15:27.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
これに懸けてんだよ 俺は

199
00:15:48.366 --> 00:15:49.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いらっしゃい

200
00:15:55.833 --> 00:15:57.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ソース焼そば

201
00:15:58.266 --> 00:16:00.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
目玉焼き載っけて

202
00:16:00.966 --> 00:16:02.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あいよ

203
00:16:19.766 --> 00:16:21.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今度の映画ね

204
00:16:22.533 --> 00:16:23.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うん

205
00:16:25.133 --> 00:16:28.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
父親と娘の話なの

206
00:16:30.533 --> 00:16:31.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
へえ

207
00:16:35.433 --> 00:16:38.233  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
