208
00:16:40.100 --> 00:16:41.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
最後には―

209
00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:48.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
再会した父親に
思いの丈をぶつけるっていう…

210
00:16:51.400 --> 00:16:52.400  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
まあ…

211
00:16:54.233 --> 00:16:59.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
大した事件も起こらない
親子の話なんだけど

212
00:17:01.133 --> 00:17:02.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
うん

213
00:17:10.766 --> 00:17:13.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
捨てられたのにさ

214
00:17:18.633 --> 00:17:20.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
恨んでないって

215
00:17:23.766 --> 00:17:27.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
逆にありがとうって

216
00:17:32.866 --> 00:17:37.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あたしが お父さんに会った時―

217
00:17:41.933 --> 00:17:47.433  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ホントに そんなこと言えるのかな

218
00:17:51.500 --> 00:17:52.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）あんた―

219
00:17:54.266 --> 00:17:57.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
親父さんのこと恨んでるのかい？

220
00:18:14.066 --> 00:18:15.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
分かんない

221
00:18:20.033 --> 00:18:22.300  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
はい おまち

222
00:18:23.166 --> 00:18:24.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いただきます

223
00:18:31.666 --> 00:18:32.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（倫子）これ…

224
00:18:36.533 --> 00:18:38.733  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
ある人が教えてくれたんだ

225
00:18:40.566 --> 00:18:42.200  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ソース焼そばに―

226
00:18:43.766 --> 00:18:50.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
四万十川の青のりをかけると
香りがよくなるんだって

227
00:19:01.366 --> 00:19:02.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いただきます

228
00:19:14.166 --> 00:19:16.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（鼻をすする音）

229
00:19:39.333 --> 00:19:40.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（マスター）どうだい？

230
00:19:45.066 --> 00:19:46.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おいしい

231
00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:52.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
これを教えてくれた人も―

232
00:19:53.433 --> 00:19:58.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あんたの大ファンなんだって

233
00:20:12.866 --> 00:20:14.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（茂樹）おまたせ

234
00:20:14.566 --> 00:20:16.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（倫子）やった！

235
00:20:16.200 --> 00:20:21.466  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
ハハッ 倫子の大好きな
四万十川の青のり

236
00:20:21.566 --> 00:20:24.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
いっぱい かけちゃおう

237
00:20:27.600 --> 00:20:30.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
それ～

238
00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:34.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
倫子 お父さんの焼そば大好き！

239
00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:38.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
やったあ！
（倫子）やったあ

240
00:20:39.833 --> 00:20:43.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
あたし お父さんのこと―

241
00:20:45.166 --> 00:20:46.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
恨んでないよ

242
00:20:49.433 --> 00:20:53.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お父さんがいたから あたし…

243
00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:12.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
お父さん

244
00:21:21.166 --> 00:21:22.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
ありがとう

245
00:21:24.133 --> 00:21:25.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
（観客）おっさん 見えねえよ

246
00:21:26.933 --> 00:21:29.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
おい おっさん

247
00:21:54.666 --> 00:21:56.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（マスター）
それからの風見倫子は―

248
00:21:57.200 --> 00:22:01.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
ますます芝居に
磨きがかかったって評判さ

249
00:22:01.866 --> 00:22:05.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
今度 海外の映画にも出るらしい

250
00:22:05.566 --> 00:22:06.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
でも…

251
00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:36.133  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
（ミキ）カナ こないだ言ってたさ
